dct_description_sm: per Casparum Henneberch Erlichensem; A. Goos sculpsit.
3 bar scales on map, given in "Miliaria parva", "...mediocira", and "...et magna".
Decorative border and cartouches, compass rose, buildings, vegetation, ships.
